No. 10-8540. Leandra Smith, aka Leanra Smith, aka Rhonda L. Barber, and Anewa Tiari-El, aka Annie B. Williams, Petitioners v. United States. 563 U.S. 1029, 131 S. Ct. 2930,

180 L. Ed. 2d 238,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 4124. May 31, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 398 Fed. Appx. 938.
